column2: SELECT s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z as redshift, s.zErr, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, zp.modelMag_u as mag_u, zp.modelMag_g as mag_g, zp.modelMag_r as mag_r, zp.modelMag_i as mag_i, zp.modelMag_z as mag_z, mag_u-mag_g as u_g, mag_g-mag_r as g_r, mag_r-mag_i as r_i, mag_i-mag_z as i_z FROM SpecObjAll as s  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) AS GN ON s.bestObjID = GN.objID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as zp ON zp.objID = s.bestObjID  WHERE  s.class = &&& AND   s.zWarning=#
